subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Shabazz Napier and Alex Oriakhi each put up double-doubles and Connecticut, playing its fourth straight game without its ailing coach Jim Calhoun, beat DePaul, 80-54, on Wednesday.
